wiki.summary: “Flooded The Face” stands proudly as the opening track of Lil Uzi Vert’s highly anticipated album, Pink Tape. Meticulously crafted over the years, this mesmerizing song originated in 2017 and underwent enhancements in 2022, showcasing Lil Uzi Vert’s unwavering commitment to perfection. The production of “Flooded The Face” bears the undeniable imprint of Harold Harper, a trusted and proven collaborator of Lil Uzi Vert. Harper’s exceptional skills shine through, elevating the song to new heights of sonic brilliance. Read more on Last.fm.
